{
  "stem": "3341.4",
  "chunk_idx": 18,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He brought me to a soldier who was willing to take me to the outskirts of the village, where they had a little command post, a small one for that, for, for that unit.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when he brought me to this hut, where the commander of this section was, he was a Jewish fellow, luckily.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he, he had somebody in the room, other soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He sent him out, he closed the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't know what he wants from me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I didn't know he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He said you are the-- you are [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I said I'm-- yeah, I made the mistake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I said to the soldier when he came towards me, I said, I am [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I had my hands up, I am [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That means I am Jew, don't shoot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I didn't know, that time, that the word [NON-ENGLISH], which means Jew, is a swear word in Russian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And by law, in Russia, the ordinary peasants were not allowed to say to somebody, you Jew, because it was a swear word.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The order by the government, not so, so much friendliness towards the Jews, but to make them more obedient, they said, you call them [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So the, the officer, the officer told me, don't say, [NON-ENGLISH], you say [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Therefore, he didn't want to obey you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because we don't say the word [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you would have said, I am [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, all right, so what's the difference?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, it's a big difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you are the first living Jew, which I have seen from [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kharkiv. ?] You know, and he cried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was a very emotional get together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I said, I want to go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I want to go to Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
